# Sūra XC.: Balad, or The City.

### Section 1

![](../gif/090/090_001.gif)

1. L<u>a</u> oqsimu bih<u>atha</u> albalad**i**

1\. I do call to witness  
This City;—

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_002.gif)

2. Waanta <u>h</u>illun bih<u>atha</u> albalad**i**

2\. And thou art a freeman  
Of this City;—

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_003.gif)

3. Waw<u>a</u>lidin wam<u>a</u> walad**a**

3\. And (the mystic ties  
of) Parent and Child;—

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_004.gif)

4. Laqad khalaqn<u>a</u> al-ins<u>a</u>na fee kabad**in**

4\. Verily We have created  
Man into toil and struggle.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_005.gif)

5. Aya<u>h</u>sabu an lan yaqdira AAalayhi a<u>h</u>ad**un**

5\. Thinketh he, that none  
Hath power over him?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_006.gif)

6. Yaqoolu ahlaktu m<u>a</u>lan lubad<u>a</u>**n**

6\. He may say (boastfully):  
"Wealth have I squandered  
In abundance!"

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_007.gif)

7. Aya<u>h</u>sabu an lam yarahu a<u>h</u>ad**un**

7\. Thinketh he that none  
Beholdeth him?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_008.gif)

8. Alam najAAal lahu AAaynayn**i**

8\. Have We not made  
For him a pair of eyes?—

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_009.gif)

9. Walis<u>a</u>nan washafatayn**i**

9\. And a tongue,  
And a pair of lips?—

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_010.gif)

10. Wahadayn<u>a</u>hu a**l**nnajdayn**i**

10\. And shown him  
The two highways?

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_011.gif)

11. Fal<u>a</u> iqta<u>h</u>ama alAAaqaba**ta**

11\. But he hath made no haste  
On the path that is steep.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_012.gif)

12. Wam<u>a</u> adr<u>a</u>ka m<u>a</u> alAAaqaba**tu**

12\. And what will explain  
To thee the path that is steep?—

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_013.gif)

13. Fakku raqaba**tin**

13\. (It is:) freeing the bondman;

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_014.gif)

14. Aw i<u>t</u>AA<u>a</u>mun fee yawmin <u>th</u>ee masghaba**tin**

14\. Or the giving of food  
In a day of privation

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_015.gif)

15. Yateeman <u>tha</u> maqraba**tin**

15\. To the orphan  
With claims of relationship,

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_016.gif)

16. Aw miskeenan <u>tha</u> matraba**tin**

16\. Or to the indigent  
(Down) in the dust.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_017.gif)

17. Thumma k<u>a</u>na mina alla<u>th</u>eena <u>a</u>manoo
wataw<u>as</u>aw bi**al**<u>ss</u>abri wataw<u>as</u>aw
bi**a**lmar<u>h</u>ama**ti**

17\. Then will he be  
Of those who believe,  
And enjoin patience, (constancy,  
And self-restraint), and enjoin  
Deeds of kindness and compassion.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_018.gif)

18. Ol<u>a</u>-ika a<u>s</u>-<u>ha</u>bu almaymana**ti**

18\. Such are the Companions  
Of the Right Hand.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_019.gif)

19. Wa**a**lla<u>th</u>eena kafaroo bi-<u>a</u>y<u>a</u>tin<u>a</u> hum
a<u>s</u>-<u>ha</u>bu almash-ama**ti**

19\. But those who reject  
Our Signs, they are  
The (unhappy) Companions  
Of the Left Hand.

------------------------------------------------------------------------

![](../gif/090/090_020.gif)

20. AAalayhim n<u>a</u>run mu/<u>s</u>ada**tun**

20\. On them will be Fire  
Vaulted over (all round).

